<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Nutmeg" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Nutmeg,</orth> the fruit of Myristica moschata: <bibl n="shak. wt 4.3.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 3, 50</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.7.20" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 7, 20</bibl>. A gilt n. a common gift at Christmas: <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.652" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 652</bibl>.
